has%20helped%20with%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20Heitsenrether%2C%20who%20is%20responsible%20for%20executing%20the%20bank's%20generative%20AI%20strategy%2C%20told%20a%20conference%20in%20New%20York%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDimon%20himself%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Btremendous%20user%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20and%20is%20waiting%20for%20the%20ability%20to%20use%20the%20bank's%20tools%20on%20his%20phone.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BHe's%20been%20desperate%20to%20get%20it%20on%20his%20phone%20and%20so%20that's%20a%20big%20deliverable%20before%20the%20end%20of%20the%20year%2C%20%26quot%3B%20Heitsenrether%20added.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EJPMorgan%2C%20America's%20largest%20bank%2C%20has%20now%20rolled%20out%20the%20LLM%20Suite%2C%20a%20generative%20AI%20assistant%2C%20to%20200%2C000%20of%20its%20employees.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20tools%20are%20the%20first%20step%20in%20adopting%20AI%20technology%20across%20the%20firm.%20Heitsenrether%2C%20JPMorgan's%20chief%20data%20and%20analytics%20officer%2C%20speaking%20at%20the%20Evident%20AI%20Symposium%2C%20said%20that%20the%20next%20generation%20would%20go%20beyond%20helping%20employees%20write%20an%20email%20or%20summarize%20a%20document%20and%20link%20the%20tools%20with%20their%20everyday%20workflow%20to%20help%20people%20do%20their%20jobs.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BBasically%20go%20from%20the%20five%20minutes%20of%20efficiency%20to%20the%20five%20hours%20of%20efficiency%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added%2C%20saying%20it%20will%20take%20time%20to%20reach%20that%20goal.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2230384350-4253-47b7-931e-6c73a74a953f%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3E'The%20flywheel%20effect'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20response%20to%20the%20LLM%20rollout%20has%20been%20%26quot%3Benthusiastic%26quot%3B%20and%20has%20created%20%26quot%3Bhealthy%20competition%26quot%3B%20between%20teams%2C%20she%20said.%20The%20wealth%20and%20asset%20management%20arm%20was%20the%20first%20division%20to%20use%20generative%20AI%2C%20piloting%20a%20generative%20AI%20%26quot%3Bcopilot%26quot%3B%20for%20its%20private%20bank%20this%20summer.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20the%20investment%20bank%20found%20out%20they%20said%20'Well%2C%20wait%20a%20minute%2C%20we%20want%20to%20be%20on%20there%20too%2C'%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt%20does%20create%20a%20flywheel%20effect.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EJPMorgan%20offers%20courses%20and%20in-person%20training%20for%20employees%20to%20use%20the%20firm's%20generative%20AI%20tools%2C%20such%20as%20how%20to%20prompt%20a%20chatbot%20properly%2C%20but%20the%20bank%20is%20also%20leaning%20on%20superusers%2C%20or%20the%2010%25%20to%2020%25%20of%20employees%20who%20are%20%26quot%3Breally%20keen%26quot%3B%20to%20help%20with%20adoption.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BWe%20embed%20people%20within%20different%20groups%20to%20be%20the%20local%20source%20of%20expertise%20to%20be%20able%20to%20help%20people%20that%20they%20work%20with%20understand%20how%20to%20adopt%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Heitsenrether%20explained.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20most%20common%20superusers%20seem%20to%20be%20those%20who%20clearly%20see%20the%20benefits%20of%20generative%20AI%2C%20such%20as%20a%20lawyer%20who%20saves%20hours%20by%20getting%20a%20synopsis%20of%20contracts%20or%20regulations%20instead%20of%20reading%20them%20all.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDespite%20Wall%20Street's%20interest%20in%20generative%20AI%2C%20getting%20workers%20to%20actually%20adopt%20the%20technology%20has%20been%20a%20key%20hurdle%20for%20finance%20firms%2C%20Accenture%20Consultant%20Keri%20Smith%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-wall-street-using-ai-generative-artificial-intelligence-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Epreviously%20told%20BI%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20training%20and%20reskilling%20efforts%20have%20come%20under%20the%20spotlight%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHeitsenrether%20said%20that%20they're%20trying%20to%20engage%20with%20the%20%26quot%3Bpockets%20of%20resistance%26quot%3B%20now%20because%20it%20will%20be%20harder%20to%20convert%20them%20once%20the%20technology%20becomes%20intertwined%20with%20workflows.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EShe%20also%20said%20that%20the%20sooner%20people%20engage%20with%20AI%2C%20the%20less%20skeptical%20they%20are%2C%20and%20they%20see%20how%20it%20can%20augment%2C%20not%20replace%2C%20their%20jobs.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BHaving%20it%20in%20your%20hands%20I%20think%20demystifies%20it%20quite%20a%20lot%2C%26quot%3B%20Heitsenrether%20said.%20She%20used%20the%20example%20of%20a%20developer%20using%20it%20to%20more%20quickly%20write%20a%20test%20case.%20She%20said%20if%20they%20see%20the%20benefits%2C%20they%20realize%20%26quot%3Bthis%20is%20not%20something%20that's%20going%20to%20be%20done%20without%20me%2C%20but%20it's%20just%20a%20way%20to%20make%20my%20work%20that%20much%20more%20effective.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22821f680c-acf0-4f26-a3d9-9ee2a53def5f%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EWhat's%20next%3A%20AI%20assistants%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBy%20this%20time%20next%20year%2C%20Heitsenrether%20told%20the%20audience%20that%20she%20hopes%20she'll%20be%20talking%20about%20%26quot%3Benabling%20employees%20with%20their%20own%20assistant%26quot%3B%20that's%20specific%20to%20them%20and%20their%20jobs.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESome%20of%20the%20legwork%20needed%20to%20develop%20those%20more%20autonomous%20forms%20of%20AI%20is%20currently%20being%20done%20in%20pilots%2C%20Sumitra%20Ganesh%2C%20a%20member%20of%20JPMorgan's%20AI%20research%20team%2C%20said%20during%20another%20panel.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEven%20still%2C%20the%20early%20use%20cases%20for%20AI%20workers%20will%20likely%20be%20constrained%20because%20these%20systems%20still%20need%20a%20human%20in%20the%20loop%20to%20ensure%20the%20reliability%20needed%20in%20such%20a%20regulated%20industry.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BWe%20don't%20have%20a%20lot%20of%20trust%20right%20now%20in%20these%20systems%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20Having%20an%20expert%20in%20the%20loop%20who%20can%20verify%20AI%20outputs%20is%20%26quot%3Bkind%20of%20babysitting%20these%20agents%20at%20this%20point%2C%20but%20hopefully%2C%20it's%20like%20training%20wheels%20%E2%80%94%20at%20some%20point%20we%20will%20be%20confident%20enough%20to%20let%20them%20go%2C%26quot%3B%20Ganesh%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjpmorgan-generative-ai-adoption-llm-suite-2024-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1732269901000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F673fb588fa0140cdd564cf55%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjpmorgan-generative-ai-adoption-llm-suite-2024-11%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20executive%20who%20oversees%20JPMorgan's%20AI%20efforts%20gives%20a%20look%20into%20how%20the%20adoption%20of%20generative%20AI%20is%20going%20down%20at%20America's%20largest%20bank.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22mabrego%40businessinsider.com%20(Michelle%20Abrego%2CBianca%20Chan)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjpmorgan-generative-ai-adoption-llm-suite-2024-11%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Employers%20are%20scrutinizing%20WFH%20accommodation%20requests%20%26amp%3Bmdash%3B%20here's%20how%20to%20make%20yours%20stronger%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223143%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Greg%20Mansell%5C%22%20chars