ts%20will%20respond%2C%20the%20team%20at%20UBS%20GWM%20gave%20it%20a%20shot%20in%20their%202025%20outlook%20report%2C%20which%20was%20released%20on%20November%2021.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20key%20focus%20of%20the%20report%20is%20how%20the%20global%20economy%20may%20be%20at%20a%20pivot%20point%2C%20following%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-invest-stock-market-international-investing-strategy-charles-schwab-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esurge%20in%20populist%20sentiment%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20culminated%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdonald-trump-wins-presidential-election-race-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eelection%20of%20Donald%20Trump%3C%2Fa%3E%20earlier%20this%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20Wall%20Street%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-invest-trump-win-election-stock-market-outlook-strategy-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eis%20confident%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20there%20will%20be%20a%20continued%20boom%20under%20Trump%2C%20UBS%20GWM%20is%20less%20sure.%20This%20new%20political%20regime%20%26quot%3Bmight%20extend%20or%20end%20the%20Roaring%2020s%2C%26quot%3B%20strategists%20remarked.%20What%20happens%20may%20depend%20in%20large%20part%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-market-outlook-trump-president-economy-tariffs-trade-war-kelly-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewhat%20happens%20with%20Trump's%20tariff%20policy%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20tariff%20shock%20could%20trigger%20a%20stagflationary%20downside%20scenario%2C%26quot%3B%20UBS%20GWM%20strategists%20said.%20%26quot%3BAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20negotiations%20with%20trading%20partners%20or%20domestic%20legal%20challenges%20might%20mitigate%20their%20scope%20and%20impact%2C%20and%20tax%20cuts%20and%20deregulation%20could%20support%20a%20more%20positive%20market%20narrative.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20that%20in%20mind%2C%20UBS%20GWM%20is%20preaching%20humility%20and%20portfolio%20diversification%20to%20its%20clients.%20After%20all%2C%20investors%20have%20seen%20how%20troubling%20global%20events%20can%20coincide%20with%20rallies%2C%20and%20vice%20versa.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20to%20be%20prepared%20for%20a%20wide%20range%20of%20outcomes%20in%20the%20year%20ahead%2C%26quot%3B%20Mark%20Haefele%2C%20UBS%20GWM's%20chief%20investment%20officer%2C%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220dac53f1-b6e3-4bb0-b9a3-3822a4e1a816%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhere%20stocks%20could%20head%20in%202025%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20four%20potential%20templates%20that%20markets%20could%20follow%20in%202025%2C%20in%20UBS%20GWM's%20view.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUBS%20GWM%20thinks%20the%20most%20likely%20outcome%20is%20that%20the%20US%20economy%20will%20continue%20to%20grow%2C%20even%20as%20tariffs%20are%20implemented%2C%20due%20to%20deregulation%20and%20bright%20sentiment%20from%20business%20leaders.%20In%20this%20backdrop%2C%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20could%20rise%20to%206%2C600%2C%20provided%20that%20inflation%20and%20interest%20rates%20also%20fall.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20prospect%20of%20lower%20taxes%20and%20deregulation%20adding%20to%20a%20positive%20'Roaring%2020s'%20market%20narrative%20built%20on%20solid%20growth%2C%20and%20continued%20investment%20in%20AI%26quot%3B%20has%20led%20to%20optimism%20in%20markets%2C%20Haefele%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20even%20more%20upbeat%20view%20is%20that%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20will%20soar%20to%207%2C000%20thanks%20to%20exceptionally%20strong%20economic%20growth%20and%20continued%20excitement%20about%20artificial%20intelligence%2C%20all%20with%20minimal%20inflation.%20Stocks%20would%20also%20benefit%20from%20lower%20taxes%2C%20fewer%20regulations%2C%20and%20trade%20deals%20that%20minimize%20the%20pain%20that%20tariffs%20could%20bring.%20Interest%20rate%20cuts%20would%20be%20the%20icing%20on%20the%20cake.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInvestors%20will%20most%20likely%20be%20satisfied%20at%20the%20end%20of%20next%20year%2C%20UBS%20GWM%20believes%2C%20as%20the%20firm%20assigned%20a%2050%25%20likelihood%20to%20its%20base%20case%20and%20a%2025%25%20chance%20to%20the%20bull%20scenario.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20there's%20about%20a%20one%20in%20four%20chance%20that%20next%20year%20is%20marked%20by%20major%20market%20losses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20so-called%20%26quot%3Btariff%20shock%26quot%3B%20scenario%20has%20about%20a%2015%25%20chance%20of%20happening%2C%20and%20it%20could%20send%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20tumbling%20to%205%2C100%20as%20a%20burgeoning%20trade%20war%20sends%20inflation%20higher%20while%20crushing%20global%20growth.%20In%20this%20backdrop%2C%20it's%20hard%20to%20see%20how%20US%20stocks%20could%20dodge%20heavy%20losses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20risk%20scenario%20is%20that%20trade%20tariffs%2C%20excessive%20fiscal%20deficits%2C%20and%20geopolitical%20strife%20will%20contribute%20to%20higher%20inflation%2C%20weaker%20growth%2C%20and%20market%20volatility%2C%26quot%3B%20UBS%20GWN%20strategists%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETariffs%20are%20far%20from%20the%20only%20risk%20to%20markets.%20An%20old-fashioned%20recession%20featuring%20a%20weaker%20jobs%20market%20and%20softer%20consumer%20spending%20could%20send%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20all%20the%20way%20back%20to%204%2C500.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228d828b51-f16f-441b-8bbb-547c4706dfce%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E8%20top%20ways%20to%20invest%20now%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20there's%20no%20way%20to%20know%20which%20of%20those%20four%20outcomes%20will%20occur%2C%20UBS%20GWM%20spotlighted%20eight%20investments%20that%20are%20likely%20to%20appreciate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETechnology%20stocks%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20are%20among%20the%20firm's%20top%20ideas%2C%20including%20semiconductor%20firms%20and%20companies%20tied%20to%20artificial%20intelligence.%20Tariffs%20could%20weigh%20on%20growth%2C%20but%20the%20sector's%20long-term%20growth%20story%20is%20likely%20intact%20regardless%20of%20what%20happens%20on%20the%20political%20policy%20front.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAI%20infrastructure%20spending%20remains%20robust%2C%20and%20we%20expect%20key%20semiconductor%20components%20needed%20for%20AI%20to%20remain%20supply%20constrained%20in%202025%2C%20supporting%20pricing%2C%26quot%3B%20UBS%20GWM%20strategists%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EUtilities%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20are%20also%20a%20less%20heralded%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-stocks-to-buy-utilities-investing-strategy-advice-goldman-sachs-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eway%20to%20ride%20AI%20momentum%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20UBS%20GWM%20noted%2C%20plus%20the%20group%20is%20defensive%20and%20could%20hold%20up%20better%20in%20a%20bearish%20scenario.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAlthough%20utilities%20companies%20with%20high%20renewables%20exposure%20could%20face%20near-term%20pressures%2C%20we%20also%20expect%20significant%20growth%20in%20AI%20data%20centers%20to%20fuel%20power%20demand%2C%20leading%20to%20higher%20power%20prices%2C%26quot%3B%20UBS%20GWM%20strategists%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20other%20sector%20that%20UBS%20GWM%20highlighted%20is%20%3Cstrong%3Efinancials%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20which%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdigital.fidelity.com%2Fprgw%2Fdigital%2Fresearch%2Fsector%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehandily%20outperformed%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20market%20in%20the%20last%20month.%20Strategists%20are%20confident%20that%20the%20group%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-invest-trump-win-election-stock-market-outlook-strategy-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emore%20room%20to%20run%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20expect%20Fed%20rate%20cuts%20to%20lead%20to%20lower%20funding%20costs%2C%20higher%20loan%20growth%2C%20and%20more%20capital%20market%20activity%2C%26quot%3B%20UBS%20GWM%20strategists%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BFollowing%20the%20US%20election%2C%20we%20also%20expect%20the%20financial%20sector%20to%20benefit%20from%20deregulation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20international%20markets%2C%20the%20firm%20is%20bullish%20on%20%3Cstrong%3EAsian%20stocks%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eoutside%20of%20Japan%20as%20interest%20rates%20fall%20in%20the%20region.%20Additionally%2C%20%3Cstrong%3Esmall-%20and%20mid-sized%20European%20stocks%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%E2%80%94%20which%20are%20relatively%20cheap%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0should%20benefit%20from%20solid%20economic%20growth%20and%20lower%20rates%2C%20though%20tariffs%20are%20a%20risk.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOutside%20of%20equities%2C%20UBS%20GWM%20recommends%20%3Cstrong%3Ehigh-quality%20bonds%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20while%20interest%20rates%20fall.%20Bond%20yields%20have%20risen%20lately%20on%20the%20back%20of%20Trump's%20win%2C%20since%20investors%20now%20expect%20higher%20growth%2C%20inflation%2C%20and%20budget%20deficits.%20This%20may%20be%20a%20good%20time%20to%20lock%20in%20higher%20rates%2C%20UBS%20GWM%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20believe%20investment-grade%20bonds%20offer%20attractive%20yields%20and%20expect%20mid-single-digit%20returns%20in%20US%20dollar%20terms%2C%26quot%3B%20UBS%20GWM%20strategists%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPrecious%20metals%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20are%20also%20worth%20owning%2C%20UBS%20GWM%20said.%20Gold%20can%20continue%20to%20rise%20to%20%242%2C900%20next%20year%2C%20in%20the%20firm's%20view%20%E2%80%94%20and%20copper%2C%20lithium%2C%20and%20nickel%20also%20appear%20to%20have%20upside.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%202025%2C%20we%20believe%20gold%20will%20remain%20an%20effective%20hedge%20against%20key%20political%20concerns%2C%20including%20government%20debt%20levels%2C%20inflation%2C%20or%20geopolitical%20tensions%2C%26quot%3B%20UBS%20GWM%20strategists%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELastly%2C%20investors%20should%20have%20exposure%20to%20%3Cstrong%3Ereal%20estate%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20in%20lig