ing%20it%20quits.%20Because%20calling%20it%20quits%20brings%20not%20only%20pain%20but%20also%20an%20acknowledgement%20that%20we%20made%20a%20mistake.%20So%2C%20we%20carry%20on%20with%20the%20burden%20of%20our%20past%20mistakes%20on%20our%20fingers%20only%20to%20dig%20our%20claws%20deeper%20into%20each%20other's%20skin.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20a%20%E2%80%98good'%20day%2C%20such%20as%20today%2C%20the%20AQI%20reading%20in%20Delhi%20is%20407.%20We%20are%20jubilant%20at%20the%20sickly%20sunshine%20trickling%20through%20the%20slightly%20dissipated%20smog.%20At%20least%20it's%20not%201600.%20At%20least%20s%2Fhe%20isn't%20hitting%20me%20in%20the%20face.%20We%20are%20so%20used%20to%20the%20drama%20of%20this%20destructive%20toxicity%20that%20we%20are%20scared%20of%20the%20lack%20of%20drama.%20Our%20lungs%20get%20into%20a%20shock%20when%20we%20are%20exposed%20to%20clean%2C%20crisp%20air%20the%20way%20we%20feel%20threatened%20by%20a%20love%20that%20does%20not%20thrive%20on%20contractual%20power%20dynamics.%20We%20are%20instinctively%20scared%20and%20suspicious.%20We%20seek%20beauty%20in%20the%20haze%20of%20smog%20exactly%20how%20we%20find%20comfort%20in%20the%20seeming%20stability%20of%20a%20marriage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20beauty%20and%20this%20stability%20are%20enough%20to%20kill%20us%20a%20hundred%20times%20over.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EPollution%2C%20Marriage%20And%20Class%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EResorting%20to%20generalisations%2C%20there%20is%20a%20class-defined%20perception%20of%20pollution%20of%20both%20marriage%20and%20air.%20While%20the%20rich%20keep%20discussing%20it%20ad%20nauseam%20from%20the%20relative%20comforts%20of%20their%20homes%E2%80%94with%20airconditioning%20and%20purifiers%20cranked%20up%20to%20max%E2%80%94the%20poor%20have%20no%20such%20luxury.%20In%20fact%2C%20they%20light%20a%20fire%20to%20keep%20them%20warm.%20The%20results%20are%20the%20same.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20rich%20have%20the%20luxury%20of%20getaways%20and%20vacations%20to%20lull%20them%20into%20thinking%20that%20it's%20not%20that%20bad.%20Or%20that%20it's%20temporary.%20The%20poor%20have%20their%20fatalism%20going%20for%20them.%20What's%20even%20the%20point%20of%20complaining%20when%20everything%20is%20awful%20anyway%3F%20This%20is%20us.%20This%20is%20how%20it%20is.%20This%20is%20how%20we%20live%20and%20die.%20The%20poor%20also%20mimic%20the%20rich%20without%20the%20safety%20net.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20recent%20report%20claims%20that%20there's%20no%20Delhi%20household%20without%20at%20least%20one%20member%20suffering%20from%20a%20pollution-related%20ailment.%20There%20are%20about%20200%20listed%20marriage%20counsellors%20in%20Delhi.%20The%20unlisted%20number%20could%20be%20even%20higher.%20And%20then%20there%20is%20the%20bevvy%20of%20family%20and%20friends%20who%20are%20ever%20so%20ready%20with%20their%20advice.%20There%20are%20at%20least%2010%2C000%20divorce%20lawyers%20in%20the%20city.%20You%20get%20the%20gist.%20Yet%2C%20it's%20a%20good%20day%20today.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt's%20very%20easy%20to%20blame%20the%20%E2%80%98other'%20for%20when%20things%20get%20ugly.%20It's%20the%20farmers%20of%20Haryana%20and%20Punjab.%20No%2C%20it's%20the%20automobiles%20in%20NCR.%20It's%20the%20other%20woman.%20Are%20you%20crazy%3F%20It's%20her%20nosy%20family%2C%20silly.%20It's%20her.%20It's%20him.%20It's%20them.%20It's%20never%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EShifting%20Goalposts%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20decide%20to%20GRAP-ple.%20We%20find%20new%20goalposts%2C%20we%20shift%20the%20old%20ones.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20reasonable.%20At%20least%20today%20is%20better%20than%20yesterday.%E2%80%9D%20And%20we%20fall%20into%20the%20old%20patterns%20when%20the%20obvious%20disasters%2C%20the%201600%20AQI%2C%20come%20down%20to%20the%20%E2%80%98reasonable'%20limits%20of%20450.%20We%20go%20back%20to%20keeping%20up%20the%20pretences%20for%20ourselves%20and%20others.%20We%20even%20celebrate%20with%20outdoor%20brunch