k%5C%22%3EAQI%20in%20the%20city%20and%20surrounding%20areas%20at%20371%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20or%20still%20in%20the%20'very%20poor'%20category%2C%20this%20morning.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20also%20underlined%20its%20intention%20to%20retain%20control%20of%20dropping%20down%20a%20level%2C%20or%20even%20two%2C%20in%20the%20GRAP%2C%20or%20Graded%20Response%20Action%20Plan%2C%20hierarchy%3B%20Justice%20Abhay%20S%20Oka%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWhat%20we%20are%20suggesting%20is%20this...%20(next)%20Monday%20we%20will%20examine%20compliance%20(of%20its%20orders%20by%20the%20Delhi%20government)...%20and%20then%20we%20will%20consider%20whether%20to%20bring%20it%20down%20from%20GRAP-IV%20to%20GRAP-II.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%2C%20today%20the%20court%20also%20proposed%20the%20government%20post%20police%20at%20the%20113%20checkpoints%20on%20the%20city's%20borders%20to%20monitor%20entry%20of%20trucks%20into%20the%20national%20capital%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20GRAP-IV%20trucks%20and%20commercial%20vehicles%20carrying%20non-essential%20goods%20and%20services%20are%20banned%20from%20entering%20the%20capital%2C%20but%20questions%20have%20been%20raised%20about%20the%20enforcement%20of%20this%20ban.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BTell%20us%20how%20you%20(the%20Delhi%20government)%20are%20stopping%20entry%20of%20trucks%3F%20We%20want%20a%20team%20of%20experts%20to%20monitor%20entry%20of%20trucks%20into%20the%20NCR%20and%20then%20we%20will%20take%20a%20call.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20dismissed%20as%20%26quot%3Barbitrary%26quot%3B%20the%20Delhi%20government's%20plea%20it%20had%2C%20in%20fact%2C%20done%20just%20that%2C%20observing%2C%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20meaningless%20if%20you're%20not%20providing%20the%20list%20of%20the%20entry%20points.%20It%20cannot%20be%20verified.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOther%20GRAP-IV%20measures%20are%20a%20ban%20on%20operation%20of%20Delhi-registered%20BS-IV%2C%20and%20older%2C%20diesel-operated%20medium%20goods%20vehicles%20(MGVs)%20and%20shifting%20of%20schools%20to%20an%20online%20mode.%20Office%20timings%20for%20government%20staff%20have%20been%20staggered%2C%20while%20private%20firms%20have%20been%20encouraged%20to%20work%20from%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fdelhi-news%2Fgrap-stages-iii-iv-revised-stricter-measures-enforced-in-delhi-ncr-7067270%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGRAP%20Stages%20III%20%26amp%3B%20IV%20Revised%2C%20Stricter%20Measures%20For%20Delhi%20NCR%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20Delhi%20residents%20have%20been%20advised%20to%20wear%20anti-pollution%20masks%20when%20leaving%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Monday%20the%20court%20said%20GRAP-IV%20would%20remain%20in%20place%20even%20if%20Delhi's%20AQI%20were%20to%20fall%20below%20450%2C%20the%20threshold%20to%20enforce%20fourth%20stage%20recommendations.%20The%20court%20had%20earlier%20criticised%20the%20Delhi%20government%20for%20failing%20to%20react%20quickly%20enough%20as%20air%20quality%20in%20the%20city%20deteriorated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdelhi-pollution-supreme-court-supreme-court-pulls-up-authorities-as-delhi-gasps-for-air-adds-a-warning-7045620%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDelhi%20Chokes%2C%20Supreme%20Court%20Flags%20%26quot%3BWrong%20Approach%26quot%3B%20In%20Enforcing%20GRAP%20Curbs%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhy%20did%20we%20wait%20for%20the%20AQI%20to%20cross%20300%3F%20How%20could%20you%20take%20such%20a%20risk%3F%26quot%3B%20the%20bench%20of%20Justice%20Oka%20and%20Justice%20Augustine%20George%20Masih%20thundered.%20This%20was%20days%20after%20the%20Delhi%20government%20invoked%20GRAP-III%20recommendations%20hours%20after%20saying%20he%20would%20not%2C%20at%20this%20stage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20-%20which%20hears%20cases%20and%20laments%20about%20Delhi's%20air%20quality%20every%20year%20-%20has%20been%20just%20as%20critical%20this%20year%2C%20particularly%20after%20the%20post-Diwali%20deterioration%20that%20is%2C%20again%2C%20an%20annual%20and%20predictable%20worsening%20of%20AQI%20after%20many%20in%20the%20city%20flout%20the%20ban%20on%20firecrackers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20earlier%20hearing%20the%20court%20bemoaned%20the%20bursting%20of%20firecrackers%20and%20came%20down%20heavily%20on%20the%20government%20and%20police%2C%20saying%20%26quot%3Bno%20religion%20encourages%20any%20activity%20which%20creates%20pollution%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20judges%20then%20held%20the%20ruling%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20and%20the%20cops%20responsible%20for%20lax%20implementation%20of%20that%20ban%20on%20firecrackers%2C%20calling%20their%20attempts%20to%20explain%20%26quot%3Beyewash%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20past%20weeks%20Delhi%20has%20woken%20up%20daily%20to%20frightening%20blankets%20of%20toxic%20smog%20(smoke%20%2B%20fog)%2C%20prompting%20repeated%20warnings%20from%20health%20experts%20about%20increased%20respiratory%20illnesses.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20AAP's%20struggles%20to%20control%20pollution%20levels%20has%20translated%20into%20ammunition%20for%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%2C%20which%20has%20attacked%20the%20ruling%20party%20ahead%20of%20February's%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20situation%20in%20Delhi%20is%20getting%20worse.%20People%20in%20Delhi%20are%20suffering%20because%20of%20the%20kind%20of%20governance%20in%20the%20city...%20dust%20control%20will%20have%20to%20be%20done%20and%20stubble%20burning%20in%20Punjab%20will%20have%20to%20stop.%20The%20situation%20of%20pollution%20is%20because%20of%20the%20Delhi%20government's%20poor%20work%20and%20the%20people%20are%20facing%20the%20consequences%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20party's%20Delhi%20unit%20boss%2C%20Virendra%20Sachdeva%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20AAP%2C%20Chief%20Minister%20Atish