%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ESAUL%20LOEB%2FGetty%2C%20Peter%20Stark%2FGetty%2C%20Tyler%20Le%2FBI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ETrump's%20proposed%20tariffs%20could%20raise%20costs%20for%20hardware%20startups%20making%20physical%20goods.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EStartups%20fear%20that%20the%20potential%20tariff%20hikes%20could%20make%20profit%20goals%20harder%20to%20reach.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EInvestors%20warn%20that%20this%20could%20lead%20large%20numbers%20of%20founders%20to%20throw%20in%20the%20towel.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20potential%20for%20increased%20tariffs%20in%20Donald%20Trump's%20second%20term%20is%20making%20hardware%20startups%20nervous%20and%20could%20push%20more%20founders%20in%20this%20tough%20sector%20to%20throw%20in%20the%20towel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20large%20retailers%20have%20begun%20to%20rejigger%20their%20supply%20chains%20to%20avoid%20the%20possible%20tariff%20hikes%20on%20Chinese%20goods%2C%20hardware%20startups%20have%20less%20room%20for%20maneuver%2C%20according%20to%20conversations%20with%20a%20dozen%20tech%20founders%20and%20investors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump's%20suggested%20tariffs%20come%20after%20four-and-a-half%20tough%20years%20for%20the%20hardware%20industry.%20The%20pandemic%20threw%20a%20wrench%20in%20the%20global%20supply%20chain.%20Investors%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpitchbook.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fhardware-vc-investing-generative-ai-rabbit-humane%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epulled%20back%20from%20hardware%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20they%20coalesced%20around%20shiny%20new%20AI%20software%20tools.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHardware%20companies%20have%20been%20through%20the%20wringer%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Nikhil%20Basu%20Trivedi%2C%20a%20general%20partner%20at%20early-stage%20investment%20firm%20Footwork.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHardware%20startups%20rely%20on%20a%20host%20of%20manufacturers%20that%20are%20mostly%20based%20in%20China.%20The%20typical%20process%20works%20something%20like%20this%3A%20A%20US-based%20startup%20with%20a%20few%20talented%20engineers%20designs%20a%20gadget%2C%20such%20as%20a%20wearable%20device.%20But%20they%20don't%20make%20this%20product.%20Instead%2C%20they%20send%20the%20design%20out%20to%20Asia%20and%20have%20another%20company%20there%20make%20prototypes%20and%2C%20if%20all%20goes%20well%2C%20mass-produce%20the%20item.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20gets%20shipped%20back%20to%20the%20US%20for%20sale.%20This%20is%20where%20Trump's%20proposed%20tariffs%20would%20likely%20kick%20in.%20When%20China-based%20manufacturers%20ship%20the%20final%20products%20back%2C%20the%20hardware%20startups%20may%20get%20hit%20with%20levees%20of%20up%20to%2060%20percent%20on%20goods%20from%20China%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fworld%2Fchina%2Fwhy-chinas-economy-is-more-vulnerable-trump-tariffs-this-time-2024-11-06%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETrump's%20statements%20during%20his%20campaign.%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJared%20Friedman%2C%20a%20group%20partner%20at%20Y%20Combinator%2C%20said%20hardware%20startups%20could%20face%20a%20major%20hurdle%20because%20critical%20components%20for%20electronics%20are%20primarily%20produced%20in%20Asia%20and%20must%20be%20transported%20globally.%20%26quot%3BThis%20isn't%20simple%20to%20fix%20because%20it's%20not%20a%20matter%20of%20replacing%20one%20supplier%2C%26quot%3B%20Friedman%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Bit's%20an%20entire%20ecosystem.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EImportal%2C%20a%20logistics%20company%20that%20helps%20businesses%20stay%20compliant%20with%20customs%20law%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20retail%20brands%20are%20asking%20the%20company%20to%20estimate%20the%20profit%20margins%20of%20new%20products%20under%20Trump's%20proposed%20tariffs%20before%20they%20even%20reach%20the%20procurement%20stage.%20%26quot%3BAnxiety%20is%20probably%20eight%20out%20of%2010%20right%20now%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Importal%20cofounder%20Graham%20Anderson%2C%20a%20former%20employee%20at%20Flexport.%20%26quot%3BI'm%20getting%20emails%20that%20are%20basically%20like%2C%20what%20can%20we%20do%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ce5d845f-ae01-4713-8128-e1091783bbe0%5C%22%3EThe%20impact%20on%20startups%3A%20'We're%20done%20here'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20aftermath%20of%20Trump's%20election%20win%2C%20euphoria%20is%20sweeping%20through%20the%20business%20world.%20Famed%20investor%20Marc%20Andreessen%20has%20likened%20Trump's%20victory%20to%20a%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmarc-andreessen-ben-horowitz-react-trump-win-crypto-founders-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eboot%20off%20the%20throat%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20while%20Elon%20Musk%2C%20as%20Trump's%20new%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-trump-tesla-spacex-x-department-government-efficiency-jobs-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20efficiency%20czar%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20has%20vowed%20to%20slash%20excess%20regulation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225136%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Elon%20Musk%20at%20a%20Trump%20rally%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F673cb2fbfa0140cdd564404e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223852%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EElon%20Musk%20became%20one%20of%20Trump's%20most%20outspoken%20supporters%20during%20his%20campaign.%3Cp%3EThe%20Washington%20Post%2FThe%20Washington%20Post%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EExcitement%20is%20tempered%20for%20those%20working%20in%20hardware%20or%20selling%20consumer%20goods.%20Tariffs%20create%20a%20gnarly%20paradox%20for%20small%20companies%3A%20While%20intended%20to%20boost%20domestic%20production%2C%20they%20can%20result%20in%20higher%20prices%20and%20softer%20customer%20demand.%20Startups%20will%20absorb%20what%20costs%20they%20can%2C%20but%20many%20will%20see%20their%20profit%20margins%20squeezed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBradley%20Tusk%2C%20a%20political%20strategist%20turned%20venture%20capitalist%2C%20highlighted%20how%20the%20pressure%20from%20tariffs%20could%20spell%20disaster%20for%20a%20certain%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20small%20startup%20definitely%20would%20be%20worse%20positioned%20to%20absorb%20the%20cost%20than%20big%20tech%2C%20but%20if%20they're%20selling%20something%20truly%20unique%20in%20the%20marketplace%2C%20it%20may%20not%20matter%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Tusk.%20He%20explained%2C%20%26quot%3BA%20truly%20unique%20product%20can%20handle%20the%20price%20increase.%20Others%20cannot.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20worst-case%20scenario%20is%20that%20tariffs%20unleash%20a%20wave%20of%20capitulation%20in%20the%20next%20few%20years%2C%20causing%20an%20unusually%20large%20number%20of%20hardware%20and%20consumer%20goods%20startups%20to%20shut%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20could%20certainly%20see%20%E2%80%94%20I%20don't%20want%20to%20call%20it%20an%20extinction%20event%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Santosh%20Sankar%2C%20a%20managing%20partner%20of%20Dynamo%20Ventures%2C%20a%20supply%20chain%20and%20mobility%20investor.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20hard%20to%20foresee%20that.%20But%20there'll%20certainly%20be%20a%20classic%20company%20that%20either%20cannot%20make%20it%20or%20maybe%20even%20chooses%20to%20say%2C%20'Hey%2C%20we're%20just%20kind%20of%20done%20here'%26quot%3B%20and%20winds%20down%20before%20the%20money%20runs%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227f6bd52a-a6fd-4143-b4de-449c073e23c3%5C%22%3ESupply-chain%20gymnastics%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ELarge%20companies%20can%20influence%20tariff%20policies%20by%20lobbying%20the%20government%20or%20seeking%20exclusions.%20During%20Trump's%20first%20presidency%2C%20Tim%20Cook%20helped%20persuade%20the%20White%20House%20to%20skip%20tariffs%20on%20most%20Apple%20products.%20Cook%20famously%20showed%20his%20thanks%20by%20sending%20Trump%20a%20Mac%20Pro.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224949%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ivanka%20Trump%2C%20Tim%20Cook%2C%20Steven%20Mnuchin%2C%20and%20Donald%20Trump%20tour%20a%20computer%20manufacturing%20facility%20where%20Apple's%20Mac%20Pros%20are%20assembled.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F673cb017ede4eeae39285f97%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223712%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETim%20Cook%20took%20Donald%20Trump%2C%20with%20Ivanka%20Trump%20and%20Steven%20Mnuchin%2C%20on%20a%20tour%20of%20the%20facility%20where%20Apple's%20Mac%20Pros%20are%20assembled%20in%20Austin%2C%20Texas%2C%20in%202019.%3Cp%3EMandel%20Ngan%2FAFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20average%20startup%20lacks%20the%20leverage%2C%20not%20to%20mention%20the%20financial%20firepower%2C%20that%20Big%20Tech%20has%20to%20influence%20policy%2C%20said%20Alan%20Deardorff%2C%20an%20economist%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Michigan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTrump%20has%20said%20he'll%20place%2010%25%20or%2020%25%20tariffs%20on%20all%20imports%20from%20everywhere%2C%20and%20certainly%20that%20would%20not%20by%20itself%20target%20or%20avoid%20startups%2C%26quot%3B%20Deardorff%20said%20in%20an%20email.%20%26quot%3BIn%20practice%2C%20he'll%20probably%20make%20many%20exceptions%20in%20response%20to%20deals%20he%20will%20make%20with%20those%20who%20will%20be%20affected%2C%20but%20presumably%2C%20startups%20will%20not%20be%20big%20enough%20to%20do%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20tech%20giants%20have%20an%20additional%20advantage%3A%20the%20budget%20to%20support%20supply%20chain%20gymnastics.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStartups%20are%20in%20a%20tight%20spot%20when%20shifting%20operations%20out%20of%20tariff-laden%20countries.%20They%20often%20go%20through%20costly%20processes%20of%20ordering%20samples%20and%20refining%20prototypes%20before%20committing%20to%20bulk%20orders%2C%20which%20puts%20a%20financial%20strain%20on%20a%20company%20that%20may%20not%20have%20any%20revenue.%20Moreover%2C%20startups%20may%20find%20themselves%20shackled%20to%20specific%20suppliers%20that%20produce%20components%20crucial%20for%20their%20products.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225525%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20red%20Tesla%20Model%203%20is%20seen%20on%20the%20assembly%20line%20at%20a%20Tesla%20factory.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F673cb003fa0140cdd5643f6e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224144%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20Tesla%20Model%203%20is%20seen%20on%20the%20assembly%20line%20at%20a%20Tesla%20factory%20in%20Fremont%2C%20California%2C%20in%202018.%3Cp%3ELea%20Suzuki%2FThe%20San%20Francisco%20Chronicle%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESpencer%20Penn%2C%20who%20helped%20develop%20the%20Model%203's%20bill%20of%20materials%20at%20Tesla%2C%20recalled%20how%20hard%20it%20was%20to%20persuade%20suppliers%20to%20make%20and%20sell%20parts%20to%20the%20automaker%20back%20in%202016.%20At%20the%20time%2C%20Tesla%20was%20delivering%20thousands%20of%20vehicles%20a%20week%20%E2%80%94%20a%20volume%20that%2C%20while%20substantial%2C%20wasn't%20convincing%20enough%20for%20suppliers%20to%20fully%20commit.%20Suppliers%20often%20prefer%20working%20with%20buyers%20who%20require%20large%20volumes%20because%20it%20can%20lead%20to%20more%20stable%2C%20long-term%20business%20relationships%20and%20higher%20efficiency.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20Penn%20is%20working%20to%20rein%20in%20the%20chaos%20of%20procurement.%20His%20startup%2C%20LightSource%2C%20offers%20software%20to%20help%20enterprises%20make%20better%20sourcing%20decisions%20and%20reduce%20import%20costs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20Trump's%20election%20win%2C%20Penn%20noted%20that%20about%20half%20of%20LightSource's%20clients%20%E2%80%94%20who%20are%20mostly%20automotive%2C%20consumer%20electronics%2C%20and%20chemical%20companies%20%E2%80%94%20have%20brought%20up%20concerns%20about%20tariffs%20or%20trade%20wars%20in%20conversations%20with%20him%20or%20his%20team.%20Some%20are%20in%20talks%20to%20go%20on%20a%20%26quot%3Bpurchasing%20spree%26quot%3B%20to%20stock%20up%20on%20inventory%20before%20potential%20new%20tariffs%20take%20effect.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChris%20Van%20Dyke's%20startup%2C%20Overview%2C%20sells%20industrial%20cameras%20that%20it%20buys%20from%20a%20Taiwanese%20supplier%20and%20spiffs%20up%20with%20software%20that%20can%20help%20identify%20defects%20on%20the%20assembly%20line.%20It%20has%20cameras%20installed%20in%20over%20a%20hundred%20facilities%2C%20making%20everything%20from%20car%20parts%20to%20sliced%20cheese.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20he's%20worried%20about%20the%20potential%20for%20Trump%20tariffs%20to%20spark%20a%20recession.%20If%20fewer%20people%20buy%20cars%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20Overview%20may%20struggle%20to%20sell%20more%20to%20domestic%20auto-part%20manufacturers.%20The%20startup's%20next%20step%20is%20to%20diversify%20where%20it%20sells%20and%20reach%20new%20customers%20in%20Europe%20and%20Asia.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20tariffs%2C%20Van%20Dyke%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20sentiment%20is%20good%2C%20the%20upside%20is%20good%2C%20but%20I%20don't%20feel%20comfortable%20just%20banking%20on%20the%20upside.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-trump-tariffs-could-impact-hardware-consumer-goods-startups-2024-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1732266061000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F673cec5cede4eeae3928791a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-trump-tariffs-could-impact-hardware-consumer-goods-startups-2024-11%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20average%20startup%20lacks%20the%20leverage%2C%20not%20to%20mention%20the%20financial%20firepower%2C%20that%20Big%20Tech%20has%20to%20influence%20Trump's%20tariffs%20policy.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22mrussell%40businessinsider.com%20(Melia%20Russell)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%