%20built%20up%20a%20healthy%20level%20of%20savings.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EShe%20began%20sharing%20her%20investing%20journey%20on%20social%20media%20through%20Instagram%20stories%20and%20received%20an%20outpouring%20of%20feedback%20and%20questions%20from%20family%20and%20friends.%20Fischer%20couldn't%20keep%20up%20with%20the%20barrage%20of%20DMs%20and%20started%20a%20TikTok%20account%2C%20%40investwithnat%2C%20to%20create%20videos%20answering%20common%20investing%20questions.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%202023%2C%20Fischer%20took%20a%20leap%20of%20faith%20and%20quit%20her%20corporate%20job%20to%20focus%20full%20time%20on%20finance%20content%20creation%20as%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fquit-big-tech-job-made-100000-revenue-within-5-months-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Esolopreneur%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20or%20a%20one-person%20business.%20Now%2C%20Fischer%20creates%20videos%20about%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Floud-budgeting-tiktok-genz-millennial-save-money-lifestyle-creep-spending-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Efinancial%20independence%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20on%20social%20media%20platforms%20and%20partners%20with%20different%20brands%20to%20create%20user-generated%20content.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EShe's%20been%20quite%20successful%3A%20so%20far%20in%202024%2C%20Fischer's%20brought%20in%20over%20%24150%2C000%20in%20revenue%2C%20contracts%20viewed%20by%20Business%20Insider%20show.%20And%20that's%20in%20an%20increasingly%20cutthroat%20creator%20economy%20%E2%80%94%20according%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.goldmansachs.com%2Finsights%2Farticles%2Fthe-creator-economy-could-approach-half-a-trillion-dollars-by-2027.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EGoldman%20Sachs%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20only%20around%204%25%20of%20content%20creators%20globally%20generate%20over%20%24100%2C000%20a%20year.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIf%20you%20want%20to%20transform%20your%20content%20creation%20side%20hustle%20into%20an%20actual%20career%2C%20Fischer%20has%20the%20following%20advice.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2228b4ccfd-dce4-43a3-91e5-78a0b762808c%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ETake%20the%20transition%20slowly%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFischer's%20success%20didn't%20emerge%20overnight.%20She%20started%20creating%20TikToks%20in%202020%20but%20didn't%20actually%20start%20money%20until%20a%20year%20and%20a%20half%20later%2C%20primarily%20through%20producing%20user-generated%20content%20for%20companies.%20From%20there%2C%20Fischer%20began%20getting%20more%20sponsorships.%20She%20did%20this%20while%20working%20her%20full-time%20job%20as%20a%20data%20analyst.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cem%3E%26quot%3B%3C%2Fem%3EThe%20best%20way%20to%20transition%20is%20to%20actually%20just%20start%20that%20project%20on%20the%20side%20while%20you're%20working%20a%20full-time%20job%20and%20basically%20wait%20to%20see%20how%20it%20goes%2C%26quot%3B%20Fischer%20told%20Business%20Insider%20in%20an%20interview.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt's%20helpful%20to%20collect%20data%20on%20how%20your%20content%20is%20performing%20and%20monitor%20progress.%20Fischer%20waited%20until%20she%20had%20a%20year%20and%20a%20half%20of%20revenue%20data%20from%20her%20side%20hustle%20before%20deciding%20to%20take%20the%20leap.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BIf%20I%20just%20quit%20my%20job%20not%20knowing%20how%20much%20money%20I%20was%20going%20to%20make%2C%20that%20would%20just%20be%20so%20stressful%2C%26quot%3B%20Fischer%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOnce%20Fischer%20realized%20the%20paychecks%20from%20her%20side%20hustle%20were%20at%20the%20same%20level%20as%20the%20paychecks%20from%20her%20corporate%20job%2C%20she%20felt%20confident%20enough%20to%20go%20all%20in.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223a7a3e16-826e-41f6-bd93-74456d54fe6a%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3EPrepare%20your%20emergency%20fund(s)%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt's%20standard%20budgeting%20practice%20to%20have%20an%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhigh-yield-savings-account-interest-rate-dropping-investing-strategy-treasurys-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eemergency%20fund%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20can%20cover%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fbanking%2Fwhat-is-an-emergency-fund%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ethree%20to%20six%20months%20of%20living%20expenses%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20As%20a%20solopreneur%2C%20Fischer%20made%20sure%20she%20had%20not%20one%2C%20but%20two%2C%20emergency%20funds%3A%20one%20for%20personal%20use%20and%20one%20for%20her%20business%2C%20with%20enough%20money%20to%20cover%20six%20months%20of%20expenses%20for%20each.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHaving%20a%20backup%20plan%20gave%20Fischer%20more%20bandwidth%20to%20focus%20on%20growing%20her%20business.%20A%20business%20emergency%20fund%20also%20ensured%20that%20Fischer%20would%20be%20able%20to%20sustain%20her%20business%20even%20if%20it%20encountered%20financial%20challenges%20as%20she%20transitioned%20to%20becoming%20a%20full-time%20content%20creator.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIf%20being%20a%20solopreneur%20didn't%20work%20out%2C%20Fischer's%20backup%20plan%20was%20to%20go%20back%20to%20the%20corporate%20world%2C%20and%20the%20emergency%20fund%20would%20help%20Fischer%20weather%20the%20financial%20transition.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BThat%20gave%20me%20a%20lot%20of%20comfort%20knowing%20that%20if%20worse%20comes%20to%20worse%2C%20I%20can%20always%20get%20another%20jo