0was%20fully%20subscribed%20on%20the%20third%20and%20final%20day%20of%20bidding%2C%20November%2022%2C%20driven%20by%20strong%20demand%20from%20retail%20investors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20mainboard%20issue%20of%20state-owned%20NTPC%20Limited's%20subsidiary%20was%20booked%201.27%20times%20by%201%20PM%2C%20as%20per%20the%20NSE%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EOverall%2C%20NTPC%20Green%20Energy%20IPO%20received%20bids%20for%2075%2C35%2C83%2C362%20shares%2C%20compared%20to%20the%2059%2C31%2C67%2C575%20shares%20available%20for%20subscription.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20retail%20portion%20of%20the%20IPO%20was%20booked%202.85%20times%2C%20while%20the%20Qualified%20Institutional%20Buyers'%20(QIBs)%20category%20was%20booked%201.21%20times.%20The%20Non-Institutional%20Investors%20(NIIs)%20subscribed%20their%20quota%20only%2047%20percent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20QIBs%20placed%20bids%20for%2031%2C34%2C78%2C316%20shares%2C%20surpassing%20the%2025%2C88%2C23%2C531%20shares%20set%20aside%20for%20them.%20The%20NIIs%20applied%20for%206%2C06%2C62%2C178%20shares%2C%20compared%20to%2012%2C94%2C11%2C764%20shares%20available%20for%20bidding.%20Retail%20investors%20placed%20bids%20for%2024%2C54%2C19%2C476%20shares%20compared%20to%208%2C62%2C74%2C509%20shares%20reserved%20for%20the%20segment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3ENTPC%20Green%20Energy's%20shares%20will%20be%20listed%20on%20both%20the%20BSE%20and%20the%20National%20Stock%20Exchange%20(NSE)%2C%20with%20the%20tentative%20listing%20date%20fixed%20as%20November%2027.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ENTPC%20Green%20Energy%20IPO%3A%20Details%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20NTPC%20Green%20Energy%20IPO%20is%20a%20book-built%20issue%20valued%20at%20Rs%2010%2C000%20crore.%20This%20issue%20consists%20entirely%20of%20a%20fresh%20issue%20of%2092.59%20crore%20shares%2C%20with%20the%20price%20band%20set%20between%20Rs%20102%20and%20Rs%20108%20per%20share.%20Retail%20investors%20can%20apply%20for%20a%20minimum%20of%20138%20shares%2C%20which%20requires%20an%20investment%20of%20Rs%2014%2C904.%20For%20small%20Non-Institutional%20Investors%20(sNII)%2C%20the%20minimum%20investment%20is%20Rs%202%2C08%2C656%2C%20for%2014%20lots%2C%20or%201%2C932%20shares.%20For%20big%20Non-Institutional%20Investors%20(bNII)%2C%20the%20minimum%20investment%20required%20is%20Rs%2010%2C13%2C472%20for%20at%20least%2068%20lots%2C%20or%209%2C384%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EIDBI%20Capital%20Market%20Services%2C%20HDFC%20Bank%2C%20IIFL%20Securities%2C%20and%20Nuvama%20Wealth%20Management%20are%20the%20appointed%20book-running%20lead%20managers%20for%20the%20NTPC%20Green%20Energy%20IPO%2C%20with%20KFin%20Technologies%20serving%20as%20the%20issue's%20registrar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ENTPC%20Green%20Energy%20IPO%3A%20Key%20dates%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20NTPC%20Green%20Energy%20IPO's%20subscription%20window%20opened%20on%20November%2019.%20The%20basis%20of%20allotment%20for%20the%20IPO%20will%20be%20determined%20on%20Monday%2C%20November%2025.%20Following%20that%2C%20refunds%20for%20unsuccessful%20applicants%20will%20be%20initiated%20on%20November%2026%2C%20while%20shares%20will%20be%20credited%20to%20successful%20bidders'%20demat%20accounts%20the%20same%20day.%20The%20listing%20of%20NTPC%20Green%20Energy%20on%20the%20stock%20exchanges%20is%20set%20to%20take%20place%20on%20November%2027.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ENTPC%20Green%20Energy%20IPO%3A%20Objectives%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3ENTPC%20Green%20Energy%20plans%20to%20utilise%20the%20proceeds%20from%20the%20IPO%20to%20invest%20in%20its%20wholly%20owned%20subsidiary%2C%20NTPC%20Renewable%20Energy%20Limited%20(NREL)%2C%20for%20the%20repayment%20or%20prepayment%2C%20in%20part%20or%20in%20full%2C%20of%20certain%20outstanding%20borrowings%20incurred%20by%20NREL.%20The%20company%20will%20also%20use%20a%20part%20of%20the%20proceeds%20to%20meet%20general%20corporate%20expenses.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3ENTPC%20Green%20Energy%20Limited%2C%20established%20in%20April%202022%2C%20is%20a%20fully-owned%20subsidiary%20of%20public%20sector%20power%20major%20NTPC%20Limited.%20The%20company%20specialises%20in%20renewable%20energy%20projects%20through%20both%20organic%20and%20inorganic%20means.%20As%20of%20August%2031%2C%202024%2C%20the%20company's%20operational%20capacity%20includes%203%2C071%20MW%20from%20solar%20and%20100%20MW%20from%20wind%20energy%20across%20six%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1732264500000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2Fcofsnf7_ntpc-logo_625x300_18_November_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbusiness-news%2Fntpc-green-energy-ipo-mainboard-issue-fully-subscribed-on-day-3-7078415%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20initial%20public%20offering%20(IPO)%20of%20NTPC%20Green%20Energy%20Limited%20was%20fully%20subscribed%20on%20the%20third%20and%20final%20day%20of%20bidding%2C%20November%2022%2C%20driven%20by%20strong%20demand%20from%20retail%20investors.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbusiness-news%2Fntpc-green-energy-ipo-mainboard-issue-fully-subscribed-on-day-3-7078415%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22SC%20seeks%20Gyanvapi%20Masjid%20Committee's%20reply%20on%20ASI%20survey%20plea%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1732264325000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-115559661%2Cimgsize-2172347.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fsc-asks-gyanvapi-masjid-committee-to-respond-to-plea-seeking-asi-survey-of-sealed-area%2Farticleshow%2F115559701.cms%22%2C%22summary