that%20saw%20the%20third%20umpire%20give%20the%20decision%20in%20the%20bowling%20side's%20favour%2C%20while%20many%20experts%20on%20social%20media%20suggested%20that%20the%20India%20batter%20was%20not%20out.%20As%20the%20debate%20around%20the%20dismissal%20continues%20on%20social%20media%2C%20former%20umpire%20Simon%20Taufel%20has%20given%20his%20definitive%20verdict.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERahul%20was%20initially%20given%20not%20out%20by%20the%20on-field%20umpire%20while%20trying%20to%20defend%20off%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Mitchell%20Starc%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1416-mitchell-starc-playerprofile%5C%22%3EMitchell%20Starc%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%2023rd%20over%2C%20following%20which%20Australia%20went%20for%20the%20DRS%2C%20as%20they%20felt%20for%20a%20caught-behind%20dismissal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20review%2C%20third%20umpire%20Richard%20Illingworth%20felt%20Rahul%20nicked%20the%20ball%20following%20a%20spike%20on%20Snicko%2C%20despite%20the%20bat%20possibly%20looked%20to%20hit%20the%20pad%20at%20the%20same%20moment.%20Despite%20Illingworth%20requesting%20a%20front-on%20angle%2C%20he%20wasn't%20provided%20one%20by%20the%20producers%20and%20had%20to%20make%20a%20decision%20through%20the%20inconclusive%20angle%20from%20behind%20the%20stumps.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUmpires%20are%20looking%20for%20conclusive%20evidence.%20There%20were%20a%20few%20gremlins%20at%20the%20start%20of%20that%20review%2C%20being%20the%20first%20Test%20where%20he%20didn't%20get%20some%20camera%20angles%20he%20was%20asking%20for%2C%26quot%3B%20Taufel%20said%20on%20the%20Channel%20Seven%2C%20the%20host%20broadcasters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3ESimon%20Taufel%3A%20%26quot%3BWe%20saw%20with%20that%20side%20on%20shot%20there%20was%20a%20spike%20on%20RTS%20with%20the%20bat%20away%20from%20the%20pad%2C%20in%20other%20words%20the%20bottom%20of%20the%20bat%20hadn't%20reached%20the%20pad.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%26quot%3BTherefore%20rolling%20that%20through%20in%20its%20natural%20course%2C%20you%20may%20have%20seen%20that%20second%20spike%20(on%20Snicko%2C%20to%20indicate%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FtY5yCYYE6s%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FtY5yCYYE6s%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%207Cricket%20(%407Cricket)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2F7Cricket%2Fstatus%2F1859816630521561316%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ENovember%2022%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20seeing%20the%20out%20decision%20being%20displayed%20despite%20the%20lack%20of%20conclusive%20evidence%2C%20Rahul%20shook%20his%20head%20while%20walking%20to%20the%20dressing%20room%20in%20disbelief%2C%20after%20making%2026%20runs%20off%2074%20balls%20in%20the%20first%20session.%20Seeing%20that%20decision-making%20leading%20to%20Rahul's%20dismissal%20also%20left%20the%20commentators%20in%20disbelief.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETaufel%20thinks%20the%20ball%20did%20kiss%20the%20edge%20of%20Rahul's%20bat%2C%20causing%20scuff%20marks%20before%20the%20bat%20went%20on%20to%20hit%20the%20pad.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRichard%20Illingworth%20had%20a%20tough%20job%20there%2C%20but%20this%20camera%20angle%20is%20probably%20the%20best%20one%20for%20me%2C%20it%20shows%20that%20the%20ball%20does%20graze%20the%20outside%20edge.%20In%20my%20view%2C%20the%20ball%20does%20graze%20the%20outside%20edge%2C%20which%20has%20caused%20the%20scuff%20marks%2C%20but%20then%20the%20bat%20goes%20on%20to%20hit%20the%20pad.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20I%20think%20from%20a%20batter's%20perspective%2C%20they%20are%20looking%20to%20see%20that%20evidence%20on%20the%20big%20screens%20as%20the%20decision%20is%20made.%20I%20think%20that's%20exactly%20why%20KL%20Rahul%20has%20a%20question%20mark%20on%20his%20mind%20and%20Richard%20Kettleborough%20as%20well.%20I%20imagine%20there%20will%20be%20an%20interesting%20discussion%20in%20the%20umpires%20room%20in%20the%20lunch%20break.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETaufel%20further%20feels%20that%20the%20second%20spike%20would've%20come%20had%20the%20footage%20rolled%20through%20further.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20saw%20with%20that%20side%20on%20shot%20there%20was%20a%20spike%20on%20RTS%20with%20the%20bat%20away%20from%20the%20pad%3B%20in%20other%20words%2C%20the%20bottom%20of%20the%20bat%20hadn't%20reached%20the%20pad%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTherefore%20rolling%20that%20through%20in%20its%20natural%20course%2C%20you%20may%20have%20seen%20that%20second%20spike%20(on%20Snicko%2C%20to%20indicate%20bat%20hitting%20pad)%20come%20through%2C%20had%20it%20been%20rolled%20all%20the%20way%20through%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20explained.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1732262400000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2Fdd17t7ng_kl-rahul-afp_625x300_22_November_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Faustralia-vs-india-2024-25%2Fwas-kl-rahul-out-or-not-out-umpiring-great-simon-taufel-puts-end-to-controversy-7078393%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Former%20umpire%20Simon%20Taufel%20put%20an%20end%20to%20the%20KL%20Rahul%20dismissal%20controversy%20in%20the%20Perth%20Test%20with%20definitive%20verdict.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Faustralia-vs-india-2024-25%2Fwas-kl-rahul-out-or-not-out-umpiring-great-simon-taufel-puts-end-to-controversy-7078393%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Canadian%20town%20at%20standstill%20over%20councillors'%20refusal%20to%20take%20oath%20of%20allegiance%20to%20King%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1732262160000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F24%2F10%2F1920x1080%2Fskynews-king-charles_6723128.jpg%3F20241021094809%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fcanadian-town-at-standstill-over-councill