er%20who%20specialised%20in%20technology%20and%20intellectual%20property%20at%20Squire%20Patton%20Boggs%2C%20a%20law%20firm%20in%20London.%20Her%20work%20primarily%20focused%20on%20general%20commercial%20matters%20as%20well%20as%20both%20contentious%20and%20non-contentious%20intellectual%20property%20law%2C%20according%20to%20the%20firm's%20website.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20her%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%2Cnoindex%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Fin%2Fsimone-white-a9965a295%2F%3ForiginalSubdomain%3Duk%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELinkedIn%20profile%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Ms%20White%20had%20experience%20working%20across%20sectors.%20She%20also%20worked%20in%20the%20in-house%20legal%20team%20of%20a%20publicly%20listed%20global%20out-of-home%20advertising%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20employment%20history%20on%20LinkedIn%20shows%20that%20she's%20been%20associated%20with%20Squire%20Patton%20Boggs%20for%20over%20three%20years.%20She%20joined%20the%20firm%20as%20a%20trainee%20solicitor%20in%20August%202021%2C%20completing%20her%20two-year%20training%20period%20before%20she%20was%20promoted%20to%20associate%20in%20September%202023.%20Before%20this%2C%20she%20gained%20experience%20as%20a%20paralegal%20at%20Clear%20Channel%20Outdoor%2C%20working%20full-time%20from%20July%202019%20to%20July%202020.%20Her%20connection%20with%20Squire%20Patton%20Boggs%20began%20earlier%2C%20during%20a%20one-month%20vacation%20scheme%20internship%20in%20July%202018%2C%20which%20further%20solidified%20her%20interest%20in%20the%20legal%20profession.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20White%20completed%20a%20fast-track%20LPC%20at%20BPP%20Law%20School%20between%20August%202020%20and%20February%202021.%20Before%20that%2C%20she%20obtained%20her%20Bachelor%20of%20Laws%20(LLB)%20degree%20from%20Newcastle%20University%20in%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20incident%20in%20Laos%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimone%20White%20was%20visiting%20Vang%20Vieng%2