Act%20(Obamacare).%20In%202016%2C%20she%20faced%20criticism%20for%20defending%20Florida's%20ban%20on%20gay%20marriage%2C%20a%20stance%20that%20attracted%20significant%20attention%2C%20particularly%20after%20the%20Pulse%20nightclub%20shooting.%20She%20was%20also%20involved%20in%20a%20legal%20dispute%20over%20custody%20of%20a%20St%20Bernard%20dog%2C%20Master%20Tank%2C%20with%20a%20Louisiana%20family%20after%20Hurricane%20Katrina.%20Accused%20of%20stealing%20the%20dog%2C%20Ms%20Bondi%20countered%20with%20claims%20of%20neglect.%20The%20case%20was%20settled%20before%20trial%2C%20and%20Master%20Tank%20was%20returned%20to%20his%20original%20family.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EAfter%20leaving%20public%20office%2C%20Pam%20Bondi%20joined%20Ballard%20Partners%2C%20a%20lobbying%20firm%20with%20ties%20to%20Trump.%20Between%202019%20and%202020%2C%20she%20represented%20Qatar%2C%20as%20disclosed%20in%20federal%20filings%20under%20the%20Foreign%20Agents%20Registration%20Act.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EA%20vocal%20Trump%20supporter%2C%20Ms%20Bondi%20played%20a%20significant%20role%20in%20defending%20him%20during%20his%20first%20impeachment%20as%20a%20senior%20adviser%20and%20lawyer.%20She%20has%20been%20heading%20the%20legal%20arm%20of%20the%20America%20First%20Policy%20Institute%2C%20a%20conservative%20think%20tank%20focused%20on%20advancing%20Trump's%20policies.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1732251420000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2F85c1efp_pam-bondi-afp-_625x300_22_November_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Ftrump-picks-pam-bondi-as-attorney-general-after-matt-gaetz-withdrawal-5-facts-7076960%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22US%20President-elect%20Donald%20Trump%20has%20nominated%20Pam%20Bondi%20as%20the%20country's%20next%20attorney%20general.%20The%20Thursday%20announcement%20came%20after%20firebrand%20Rep.%20Matt%20Gaetz's%20withdrawal%20from%20consideration%20amid%20allegations%20of%20sexual%20m