While%20there%20weren%E2%80%99t%20any%20project%20overlaps%2C%20we%20met%20frequently.%20During%20our%20discussions%2C%20we%20realised%20that%20even%20the%20most%20ardent%20climate%20enthusiast%20we%20knew%20hadn%E2%80%99t%20gone%20solar.%20That%20was%20our%20inflection%20point.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20asked%20ourselves%20if%20they%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20do%20it%2C%20what%20are%20the%20odds%20for%20regular%20people%2C%20for%20whom%20solar%20is%20often%20just%20a%20peripheral%20consideration%3F%20It%20became%20clear%20that%20there%20needed%20to%20be%20a%20much%20better%20way%20to%20make%20solar%20energy%20easy%20and%20accessible%20for%20everyone%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcampaign.thebetterindia.com%2Fbetapadhaodeshjagao%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22BetaPadhaoDeshJagao%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FBetaPadhaoDeshJagao-desktop-1732080268.jpg%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fa%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20emerged%20was%20an%20idea%20for%20a%20startup%20based%20on%20the%20fact%20that%20white-collar%20professionals%20like%20them%20did%20not%20have%20access%20to%20a%20rooftop.%20Young%20professionals%20like%20Mathew%20and%20Naseer%20mostly%20lived%20in%20rented%20apartments%20and%20frequently%20moved%20between%20cities.%20As%20individuals%2C%20the%20economic%20factors%20and%20the%20challenges%20associated%20with%20installing%20solar%20panels%20were%20significant.%20However%2C%20they%20wanted%20to%20contribute%20to%20climate%20action%20and%20wanted%20an%20avenue%20to%20do%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20following%20year%2C%20Mathew%20joined%20hands%20with%20Naseer%20and%20his%20college%20batchmate%20Tarun%20Joseph%2C%20a%20specialist%20in%20UX%20Design%2C%20to%20establish%20%E2%80%98SundayGrids%E2%80%99%20%E2