18-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FSundayGrids-Project-1732196918-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FSundayGrids-Project-1732196918-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FSundayGrids-Project-1732196918-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-381895%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThus%20far%2C%20SundayGrids%20claims%20to%20have%20over%20600%20subscribers%20on%20their%20community%20solar%20plants.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20EV%20user%20in%20Mumbai%20describes%20purchasing%200.85%20kW%20of%20solar%20capacity%20in%20a%20project%20commissioned%20in%20the%20city%2C%20paying%20Rs%2052%2C000.%20He%20notes%2C%20%E2%80%9CIf%20you%20are%20an%20EV%20(electric%20vehicle)%20owner%20and%20do%20not%20have%20access%20to%20a%20rooftop%20to%20install%20solar%2C%20then%20it%20makes%20sense%20to%20buy%20some%20wattage%20from%20SundayGrids.%20If%20you%20want%20to%20invest%20money%20for%20returns%2C%20this%20is%20not%20the%20right%20avenue.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Akshat%20Jain%2C%20a%20financial%20consultant%20on%20LinkedIn%2C%20took%20a%20trial%20of%20the%20Cosmos%20145%20community%20solar%20project%20near%20Bengaluru%20where%20he%20reserved%203%2C277W%20(3.2%20kW)%20at%20Rs%201.6%20lakh.%20While%20Akshat%20elaborates%20on%20the%20electricity%20bill%20savings%2C%20return%20on%20investment%2C%20and%20tax%20savings%2C%20he%20also%20elaborates%20on%20the%20potential%20risk%2C%20and%20that%E2%80%99s%20important%20to%20ascertain%20before%20buying%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EGrowing%20leaps%20and%20bounds%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThus%20far%2C%20SundayGrids%20claims%20to%20have%20over%20600%20subscribers%20on%20their%20community%20solar%20plants%20and%20built%20around%2080