%2Famp%2Fthales-faces-bribery-and-corruption-investigation-13257991%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Man%20arrested%20over%20fatal%20Donegal%20service%20station%20explosion%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1732202400000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F24%2F11%2F1920x1080%2Fskynews-donegal-explosion-arrest_6753768.jpg%3F20241121142418%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fman-arrested-over-fatal-donegal-service-station-explosion-13257917%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20man%20has%20been%20arrested%20over%20an%20explosion%20in%20Donegal%20which%20killed%2010%20people%20in%202022.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A5%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fman-arrested-over-fatal-donegal-service-station-explosion-13257917%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fman-arrested-over-fatal-donegal-service-station-explosion-13257917%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fman-arrested-over-fatal-donegal-service-station-explosion-13257917%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Doctors%20Demand%20Rahul%20Gandhi's%20Apology%20Over%20%26quot%3BMemory%20Loss%26quot%3B%20Remark%20On%20Biden%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20group%20of%20medical%20practitioners%20has%20demanded%20a%20public%20apology%20from%20Congress%20leader%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20over%20his%20alleged%20disparaging%20remarks%20on%20the%20cognitive%20abilities%20of%20US%20President%20Joe%20Biden%2C%20saying%20it%20suggests%20a%20lack%20of%20sensitivity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20letter%20to%20former%20Congress%20chief%20and%20Rahul%20Gandhi's%20mother%20Sonia%20Gandhi%2C%20All%20India%20President%20of%20the%20National%20Medicos%20Organisation%20Bharat%20(NMO-Bharat)%20C%20B%20Tripathi%20said%20Rahul%20Gandhi's%20comments%20perpetuate%20harmful%20stereotypes%20about%20ageing%20and%20cognitive%20health.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20a%20poll%20rally%20in%20Maharashtra's%20Amravati%20on%20November%2016%2C%20Leader%20of%20the%20Opposition%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20said%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20appears%20to%20be%20suffering%20%26quot%3Bmemory%20loss%26quot%3B%20like%20the%20%26quot%3Bformer%20President%26quot%3B%20of%20the%20US%2C%20apparently%20referring%20to%20Biden%2C%20the%20outgoing%20president%20of%20the%20United%20States%20of%20America.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETripathi%20said%20in%20the%20letter%2C%20%26quot%3BSuch%20statements%20on%20a%20public%20platform%20risk%20perpetuating%20misinformation%2C%20potentially%20shaping%20public%20perceptions%20in%20ways%20that%20could%20negatively%20impact%20the%20understanding%20and%20treatment%20of%20actual%20patients.%26quot%3B%20The%20NMO-Bharat%20is%20deeply%20troubled%20by%20the%20remarks%20attributed%20to%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20%26quot%3Bwhich%20appeared%20to%20disparage%20the%20cognitive%20abilities%20of%20the%20President%20of%20the%20United%20States%2C%20Joe%20Biden%26quot%3B%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20disappointing%20to%20see%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20comment%20so%20crudely%20about%20a%20foreign%20head%20of%20state%20who%20is%20much%20senior%20and%20older%20than%20him.%20This%20flies%20right%20in%20the%20face%20of%20our%20Indian%20ethos%20of%20respecting%20our%20elders.%20Such%20remarks%20are%20unbecoming%20of%20a%20leader%20of%20opposition%20and%20suggest%20a%20lack%20of%20understanding%20and%20sensitivity%2C%26quot%3B%20Tripathi%20said%20in%20the%20letter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERahul%20Gandhi's%20comments%20also%20veer%20into%20ageist%20territory%2C%20perpetuating%20harmful%20stereotypes%20about%20ageing%20and%20cognitive%20health%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20not%20just%20disrespectful%20to%20the%20individuals%20targeted%20but%20also%20to%20countless%20senior%20citizens%20in%20India%20who%20contribute%20meaningfully%20to%20society%20despite%20health%20challenges%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20letter%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMrs.%20Gandhi%2C%20you%20have%20personally%20been%20a%20victim%20of%20such%20health-related%20rumours%2C%20misinformation%2C%20and%20allegations.%20You%20would%20know%20how%20damaging%20such%20narratives%20can%20be%2C%20not%20only%20for%20the%20individuals%20targeted%20but%20also%20for%20the%20broader%20discourse%20in%20society.%20This%20gives%20us%20confidence%20that%20you%2C%20of%20all%20people%2C%20can%20understand%20why%20your%20son's%20remarks%20were%20both%20unfortunate%20and%20misguided%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20letter%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOn%20behalf%20of%20the%20medical%20community%2C%20we%20urge%20Mr%20Gandhi%20to%20reflect%20on%20his%20remarks%2C%20issue%20a%20public%20apology%2C%20and%20refrain%20from%20making%20such%20insensitive%20comments%20in%20the%20future.%20Political%20dialogue%20should%20uplift%20and%20unite%2C%20not%20stigmatise%20or%20mock%2C%26quot%3B%20Tripathi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1732201500000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2Fg2ibmuqo_rahul-gandhi-ani_625x300_09_October_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdoctors-demand-public-apology-from-rahul-gandhi-over-disparaging-remarks-against-joe-biden-7073595%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20group%20of%20doctors%20has%20demanded%20a%20public%20apology%20from%20Congress%20leader%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20over%20his%20alleged%20disparaging%20remarks%20on%20the%20cognitive%20abilities%20of%20US%20President%20Joe%20Biden%2C%20saying%20it%20suggests%20a%20lack%20of%20sensitivity.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdoctors-demand-public-apology-from-rahul-gandhi-over-disparaging-remarks-against-joe-biden-7073595%22%2