0by%20modern%20agriculture%E2%80%99s%20reliance%20on%20monocultures%20and%20high-yield%20varieties.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20data%20from%20the%20International%20Union%20for%20Conservation%20of%20Nature%20(IUCN)%2C%20more%20than%20one%20in%20three%20tree%20species%20worldwide%20faces%20extinction.%20This%20genetic%20erosion%20is%20wiping%20out%20seed%20varieties%20at%20a%20rapid%20pace.%20And%20seed%20banks%20are%20a%20potential%20antidote%20to%20this%20problem%2C%20preserving%20a%20wide%20array%20of%20plant%20genetics%2C%20and%20providing%20a%20resource%20for%20reintroducing%20species.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Darlapudi%20breaks%20down%20the%20nuances%20of%20seed%20preservation%20to%20his%20audience%20of%20enthusiastic%20farmers%2C%20the%20process%20promises%20intrigue.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Ffabric-business-Tohfa-6-1732015271.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Darlapudi%20Ravi%20is%20preserving%20indigenous%20seeds%20that%20when%20planted%20will%20give%20rise%20to%20fruits%20and%20vegetables%20loaded%20with%20health%20benefits%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Ffabric-business-Tohfa-6-1732015271.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Ffabric-business-Tohfa-6-1732015271-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Ffabric-business-Tohfa-6-1732015271-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Ffabric-business-Tohfa-6-1732015271-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Ffabric-business-Tohfa-6-1732015271-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-381102%5C%22%20height%3D%5