collection%2C%20Darlapudi%20uses%20a%20varied%20array%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F189462%2Fdebal-deb-seed-bank-conserves-native-rice-variety-inspiring-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epreservation%20methods%3C%2Fa%3E.%20These%20range%20from%20potting%20the%20seed%20in%20mud%20or%20a%20bamboo%20container%20or%20applying%20soil%20to%20the%20seed%20and%20keeping%20it%20in%20the%20shade.%20But%20one%20of%20his%20favourite%20methods%20is%20coating%20the%20seed%20with%20ash.%20%E2%80%9CSome%20varieties%20like%20pumpkin%20or%20creepers%20come%20with%20slurry%20inside.%20Ash%20from%20burning%20dried%20cow%20dung%20is%20applied%20to%20the%20seeds%20and%20they%20are%20kept%20in%20bamboo%20containers%20or%20mud%20pots.%20This%20ash%20acts%20as%20a%20layer%20of%20protection%20for%20the%20seeds%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%20The%20seeds%20remain%20viable%20even%20after%20three%20years.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Fseed-preservation-Darlapudi-Ravi-1732015410.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Darlapudi%20has%20preserved%20over%203600%20varieties%20of%20indigenous%20seeds%20from%20tribal%20belts%20across%20India%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Fseed-preservation-Darlapudi-Ravi-1732015410.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Fseed-preservation-Darlapudi-Ravi-1732015410-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Fseed-preservation-Darlapudi-Ravi-1732015410-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Fseed-preservation-Darlapudi-Ravi-1732015410-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F