very%20allowed%20farmers%20to%20grow%20%3Cem%3Emakhana%3C%2Fem%3E%20like%20any%20other%20crop%20in%20fields%2C%20reducing%20dependence%20on%20deep%2C%20flood-prone%20ponds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Kumar%20also%20developed%20a%20high-yielding%20variety%20of%20%3Cem%3Emakhana%3C%2Fem%3E%20called%20%E2%80%98Swarna%20Vaidehi%3Cem%3E%E2%80%99%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20a%20high-yielding%20variety%20of%20%3Cem%3Emakhana%3C%2Fem%3E.%20This%20variety%20adapted%20well%20to%20local%20conditions%20and%20significantly%20increased%20productivity.%20Additionally%2C%20techniques%20like%20nursery%20raising%20(growing%20seedlings%20separately%20before%20transplanting)%20and%20line%20planting%20(organised%20sowing%20in%20rows)%20were%20introduced.%20These%20methods%20reduced%20seed%20requirements%20and%20improved%20yields%2C%20making%20farming%20more%20efficient.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EOvercoming%20the%20flood%20challenge%20with%20innovative%20net%20fencing%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFloods%20have%20long%20been%20a%20major%20threat%20to%20%3Cem%3Emakhana%3C%2Fem%3E%20farming%2C%20often%20destroying%20entire%20crops.%20Dr%20Kumar%20tackled%20this%20issue%20by%20introducing%20net%20fencing%2C%20a%20simple%20yet%20effective%20solution.%20It%20involves%20installing%20mesh%20barriers%20around%20%3Cem%3Emakhana%20%3C%2Fem%3Efields%20to%20protect%20crops%20from%20being%20washed%20away%20by%20floodwaters.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201280px)%20100vw%2C%201280px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Fimage_11zon-1731671497.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Mesh%20barriers%20around%20makhana%20fields%20safeguard%20crops%20from%20flood%20damage%2C%20ensuring%20a%20secure%20harvest.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%