%20often%20wiped%20out%20his%20crops%2C%20leaving%20him%20disheartened.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202020%2C%20Dhirendra%20attended%20a%20%E2%80%98Farmer-Scientist%20Interaction%20cum%20Field%20Day%E2%80%99%20organised%20by%20NRCM%2C%20where%20he%20learned%20about%20%3Cem%3Emakhana%3C%2Fem%3E%20farming.%20Inspired%20by%20the%20crop%E2%80%99s%20potential%2C%20he%20decided%20to%20switch%20from%20rice%20to%20%3Cem%3Emakhana%3C%2Fem%3E%20cultivation%20on%20his%20three-hectare%20plot%2C%20thus%20becoming%20a%20key%20case%20study%20of%20Dr%20Kumar.%20With%20technical%20guidance%20from%20NRCM%20and%20Krishi%20Vigyan%20Kendra%20(KVK)%2C%20he%20planted%20Swarna%20Vaidehi%20seeds%20in%20a%20nursery%20and%20later%20transplanted%20them%20into%20his%20fields.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20initial%20challenges%20with%20nutrient%20management%2C%20Dhirendra%20harvested%2048%20quintals%20of%20%3Cem%3Emakhana%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%20the%20first%20season%2C%20earning%20a%20gross%20income%20of%20Rs%205.28%20lakhs%20and%20a%20net%20income%20of%20Rs%202.58%20lakhs.%20This%20was%20a%20dramatic%20improvement%20compared%20to%20the%20Rs%2060%2C000%20he%20earned%20from%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F324920%2Fbrothers-biodegradable-animal-friendly-rice-agri-waste-tableware-cutlery-plates-glass%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20rice%20farming%20%3C%2Fa%3Eon%20the%20same%20land%20in%20previous%20years.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EPolythene%20lining%20as%20a%20simple%20solution%20to%20water%20management%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20technique%20that%20further%20boosted%20Dhirendra%E2%80%99s%20success%20was%20polythene%20lining%20to%20prevent%20water%20loss%20from%20lateral%20seepage.%20Traditionally%2C%20%3Cem%3Emakhana%3C%2Fem%3E%20farmers%20struggled%20to%20maintain%20consistent%20water%20levels%20in%20their%20fields%2C%20especially%20during%20the%20dry%20pre-monsoon%20months%20(March%20to%20May).%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Kumar%20recommended%20using%20100-micron%20polythene%20sheets%20to%20seal%20the%20bunds%20(field%20barriers).%20This%20simple%2C%20low-cost%20solution%20minimised%20water%20seepage%2C%20reducing%20the%20need%20for%20frequent%20irrigation.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20Dhirendra%20saved%20both%20water%20and%20costs%2C%20making%20his%20farming%20process%20more%20sustainable.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%20690px)%20100vw%2C%20690px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Fimage-3_11zon-1731671481.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22690%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20farmer%20harvesting%20makhana%20from%20a%20well-managed%20field%2C%20showcasing%20the%20increased%20yields%20and%20improved%20income%20resulting%20from%20modern%20farming%20techniques.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Fimage-3_11zon-1731671481.jpg%20690w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Fimage-3_11zon-1731671481-300x169.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Fimage-3_11zon-1731671481-500x281.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Fimage-3_11zon-1731671481-150x84.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-380418%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22388%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EFarmers%20are%20increasing%20income%20and%20yields%20with%20improved%20makhana%20farming%20methods.%3Cbr%3EImage%20courtesy%20India%20Today%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20game-changer%20for%20Bihar%E2%80%99s%20farmers%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJust%20like%20Dhirendra%2C%20many%20farmers%20across