0Quality%20Mushroom%20Farm.%20%E2%80%9CSome%20years%20ago%2C%20my%20mother%20was%20diagnosed%20with%20breast%20cancer.%20We%20had%20read%20somewhere%20that%20mushrooms%20are%20helpful%20for%20people%20suffering%20from%20breast%20and%20prostate%20cancer.%20So%2C%20when%20Trupti%20wanted%20to%20take%20this%20up%20as%20a%20full%20time%20job%2C%20it%20really%20spoke%20to%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Bhushan%20Dhakate%2C%20Trupti%E2%80%99s%20husband.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EOvercoming%20obstacles%20for%20a%20sustainable%20future%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20she%20finally%20launched%20her%20business%20in%202018%20after%20years%20of%20research%2C%20Trupti%E2%80%99s%20primary%20challenge%20became%20educating%20the%20public%20about%20mushrooms%2C%20particularly%20oyster%20mushrooms.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20had%20to%20educate%20people%20about%20the%20nutritional%20value%20of%20mushrooms%20and%20clear%20up%20misconceptions%20about%20them%20being%20a%20non-vegetarian%20food.%20I%20even%20started%20cooking%20dishes%20with%20mushrooms%20as%20the%20main%20ingredient.%20We%20went%20to%20the%20local%20markets%2C%20set%20up%20tasting%20stations%2C%20and%20handed%20out%20free%20samples.%20It%20was%20a%20lot%20of%20work%2C%20but%20slowly%20people%20began%20to%20accept%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20Trupti%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%20780px)%20100vw%2C%20780px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-11-15-at-4.36.45-PM-1731675369-edited-1731675593.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22780%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Large%2C%20high-quality%20mushrooms%20grown%20using%20organic%20methods%2C%20harvested%20by%20the%20farm%20to%20promote%20sustainable%20farming%20practices.%5C%22%20src